EXTRACTED VALUE: Saying this game looks nearly photorealistic is no understatement, as throughout most of the race, it could pass as just that.
There is little fault to be found in this game as the fighting is balanced and there are lots of engaging aspects of the title that demand your time.
Infinity Ward took the bar, threw it up, and jumped over it when it was still in the air.
If you are a fan of fun you need Burnout Paradise.
